(143, 1, '2021-06-21 19:45:59', '2021-06-21 19:45:59', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This tool should go without saying. But if I have to explain — you&nbsp;<strong>need</strong>&nbsp;this tool. I use it 24/7 — literally. Dropbox is where I store my personal &amp; business related data. It\'s accessible anywhere, and regularly backs up my important information.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Because my data is accessible anywhere, Dropbox allows me to work on a client project at home, on the bus, in a coffee shop, or at a friend\'s house. It\'s truly a gem of a tool, and I think you\'ll believe me.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Dropbox', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'dropbox', '', '', '2021-06-21 19:45:59', '2021-06-21 19:45:59', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=resource&#038;p=143', 0, 'resource', '', 0),
